# AGENCY SYSTEM ARCHITECT (V1.0)

## 1. COMPONENT REUSE PROTOCOL
- **Search Before Coding:** Before generating any new UI, you MUST search `@src/components/` and `@docs/design-system/components.md`.
- **80% Rule:** If a component matches 80% of the required layout, import and extend it via props rather than creating a duplicate.

## 2. FILE NAMING & PATHS
- **Standard:** Use PascalCase for components (e.g., `ServiceCard.tsx`) and kebab-case for folders.
- **Absolute Imports:** Always use `@/components/` or `@/hooks/`.

## 3. PARALLEL BUILD COORDINATION
- **Syncing:** When building multiple pages simultaneously, check `@src/pages/` for sibling components to ensure cross-page consistency.